text: Been ordering here a few times and I just love that it’s convenient to cook. Just throw meat + water & herbs and voila! It’s done, ordered pork bone soup packet for my sister and she loves it so much.
Great place to get Chinese herbs for soup! Well stocked. Clear instructions on packaging too for those who are not familiar with how to cook.

They offered delivery services during the circuit breaker period (and now as well), which is a huge saver as I tried to minimize going outdoors. Ordering and delivery process were also easy and smooth. I whatsapp my order, confirm the price and delivery will usually arrive in the next 2 days.

Their selection is quite huge, so far I have no problems in getting what I need.
They even retail snow chrysanthenum tea leaves. Bought some of their snow chrysanthenum and mushrooms.
Soup is flavourful! You can taste the quality!
